    suggested_client_reply:{drafted_for:'Aditya Sharma',to:'Radhika & Manan',body:'Hi Radhika & Manan — hope you\'re both doing well! I wanted to share a planning update as we head into May. We\'ve been working on your Sterling Aravalli timeline and have some exciting vendor options to share. Could we schedule a call this week? — Aditya'}
